Fig.~\ref{fig6} is the one obtained from 
TBA, Eq.~(\ref{m0sG-TBA}) and Fig.~\ref{fig7} from 
TBA, Eq.~(\ref{1e-bsG-TBA}) modified for $\chi > \pi/3$.

